{"tid":847214,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"環保撚請入嚟","createTime":"2018-10-04T04:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T04:17:31.000Z","uid":103325,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0e3dc4b691e6cdc20c1e355c9281bdb826e1159a","tid":847214,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"今朝響 KFC 堂食一份早餐，佢地好撚環保咁唔俾個熱飲杯蓋我，但其實睇返份餐，除咗個膠托蓋係循環再用外，其餘全部都係用完即棄嘅 <br />\n就算堂食佢都係俾膠餐具，膠碗膠碟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實 d 塑膠用品整咗出嚟就要用架啦，唔通整咗出嚟用都唔用就送去堆填區咩<br />\n你地要禁嘅，就應該禁止製造塑膠用品，而唔係禁止我地用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/121431_a03fd88fc2bbff1e29778ecb254531a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F121431_a03fd88fc2bbff1e29778ecb254531a9.jpg&h=ed431b41&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}